{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2d6f4ea3cf","title":"会见斯里兰卡总理班达拉奈克夫人时的谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"836b8ae6c2","index":0,"year":1972,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"2bffb53b5b","name":"对外关系和政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"cce608ea44","name":"林彪","type":"主题"},{"id":"ff3246377b","name":"批陈整风和批林批孔","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"482908a210","type":"title","text":"会见斯里兰卡总理班达拉奈克夫人时的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"a972b78376","type":"paragraph","text":"会见斯里兰卡总理班达拉奈克夫人时的谈话（节录）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"17116c0638","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"81ce6bc7e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（未经本人审阅）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"f75185ae90","type":"paragraph","text":"1972.06.28","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"9dda366428","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我们这个国家也有人家骂我们，说是整了左派。我们的“左派”是什么一些人呢？就是火烧英国代办处的那些人。今天要打倒总理，明天要打倒陈毅，后天","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"b66ca8e9f2","type":"paragraph","text":"要打倒叶剑英。这些所谓“左”派现在都在班房里头。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"6918a15bee","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来：头子在班房里。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"75393f50a6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那些年轻人是受骗的。我们这里早几年天下大乱，你还不知道呢。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"2bffd79aab","type":"paragraph","text":"班：我听说了一点。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"4b386caac6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：全国各地都打，全面，内战，就是ALl-ROUND CIVIL WAR。 现在好多了。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"6735382eba","type":"paragraph","text":"班：就是自己人之间打内战吗？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"c277718323","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：两边都发枪，一共发了一百万支枪吧。这一派军队支持这一派，那一派军队支持那一派，打。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"f795a22b44","type":"paragraph","text":"周：名义上是抢枪，实际上是送枪。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"e5e5c81f92","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：他们外交部，她们（指王海容、唐闻生）这一派是“右”派，就是保守派，靠边站，弄得吃不下饭，睡不着觉。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"a95109b354","type":"paragraph","text":"班：为什么？","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"35460aa5fb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：被那些“左”派夺了权。一个半月，权不在我们手里，在那些所谓“左”派的手里。这些所谓左派，其实就是反革命。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"7333d769fe","type":"paragraph","text":"没有多少问题，几个月过去了，几年过去了，总后台的人现在也过去了，叫林彪。（班夫人点头）坐一架飞机往苏联去，其目的是想见上帝。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"ea26bd59f9","type":"paragraph","text":"班：见上帝？","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"666aa080d3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：是啊，摔下来了，见上帝去了。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"81fc35b516","type":"paragraph","text":"班：噢，我明白了。（众笑）后来飞机怎么样了？我不大清楚。飞机掉下来了，","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"976efe81d6","type":"paragraph","text":"还是过到苏联去了？","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"f651096fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我也不知道。他自己要摔。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"},{"id":"c31459cdcc","type":"paragraph","text":"（外交部绝密文件，文特69）","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf"}],"page":{"id":"f02abeab28","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2d6f4ea3cf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}